<h3>Please introduce yourself ...</h3>

<% form_for(@submission) do |f| %>
  <%= f.error_messages %>

<%= javascript_include_tag 'jquery-1.4.4.min', 'jquery.textbox-hinter.min','form_hints' %>

<div class="submission-area">

	Hello, my name is	
	<%= f.text_field :full_name, :class => "full_name" %>
	and I am in the Department of
	<%= f.text_field :department, :class => "department" %>
	. I would love to join the fair to promote my research. For my contact information on the shirt please include:
	<%= f.text_area :office_address, :class => "office_address" %>
	, 
	<%= f.text_field :phone_number, :class => "phone_number" %>
	,
	<%= f.text_field :email_address, :class => "email_address" %>
	. I have also given the key topics I would like to appear on my shirt below. For my self and my helpers at the expo I will need
  <div class="tshirt-sizes">	
	<%= f.text_field :shirt_size_s, :value => 0 %>
	small shirts,
	<%= f.text_field :shirt_size_m, :value => 0 %>
	medium shirts,
	<%= f.text_field :shirt_size_l, :value => 0 %>
	large shirts and 
	<%= f.text_field :shirt_size_xl, :value => 0 %>
	extra-large shirts.
	</br>
	Thanks!
	</br></br>
	<%= f.text_area :small_words, :class => "small_words" %>
	<%= f.text_area :medium_words, :class => "medium_words" %>
	<%= f.text_area :large_words, :class => "large_words" %>
</div>
Thanks!

	</br></br></br>	
	<div class="actions">
    <%= f.submit %>
	</div>
</div>

<% end %>
